        ]
      },
      {
        "text": "declaring his will to have it applied to all believers;",
        "footnote": 236,
        "references": [
          {
            "reference": "John 3:16",
            "text": "For God so loved the world, that he gave his only begotten Son, that whosoever believeth in him should not perish, but have everlasting life."
          },
          {
            "reference": "John 17:9, 20, 24",
            "text": "I pray for them: I pray not for the world, but for them which thou hast given me; for they are thine.... Neither pray I for these alone, but for them also which shall believe on me through their word.... Father, I will that they also, whom thou hast given me, be with me where I am; that they may behold my glory, which thou hast given me: for thou lovedst me before the foundation of the world."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "text": "answering all accusations against them,",
        "footnote": 237,
        "references": [
