      {
        "text": "and procuring for them quiet of conscience, notwithstanding daily failings,",
        "footnote": 238,
        "references": [
          {
            "reference": "Romans 5:1-2",
            "text": "Therefore being justified by faith, we have peace with God through our Lord Jesus Christ: By whom also we have access by faith into this grace wherein we stand, and rejoice in hope of the glory of"
